		<td width="600" height="50" colspan="3" align="center" valign="middle" bgcolor="#00aeef" style="font-family:'Century Gothic',Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:22px;line-height:26px;color:#ffffff"><a href="http://ncsthechallenge.org/jobs" style="text-decoration:none;color:#ffffff;font-weight:bold" target="_blank">FIND OUT MORE</a></td>
		
		</tr>
		
		<tr>
		
		<td width="600" height="25" colspan="3" align="center" valign="top"></td>
		
		</tr>
		
		<tr>
		
		<td width="25" align="left" valign="top"></td>
		
		<td width="550" align="left" valign="top" style="font-family:'Century Gothic',Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:15px;line-height:20px;color:#222222">
			
			<table width="550" align="center" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0"><tbody><tr>
			
			<td align="left" valign="top"><a href="http://www.ncsthechallenge.org/images/photos/ncstc_staff-sideimg-group2_211014.jpg" target="_blank"><img src="https://staffing.the-challenge.org/assets/2_staff_(hoodies).jpg" alt="" width="200" height="300" border="0"></a></td>
			
			<td align="left" valign="top"><p>The Challenge is the UK's biggest provider of NCS; an exciting youth and community programme which combines outdoor activities, skill development and community volunteering. We have paid positions available for all entry levels, from those wishing to gain further experience in a youth work setting, to experienced Project Managers, Teachers and Youth Workers.</p>
			
			<p>This is a fantastic opportunity for talented, enthusiastic and experienced individual wishing to work with young people and make a difference within their communities.</p>
			
			<p>Please feel free to forward this email to anyone who might be interested!</p></td>
			
			</tr></tbody></table>

		</td>
		
		<td width="25" align="left" valign="top"></td>
		
